Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.43,0:23:42.42,ZW,NTP,0,0,0,,水…水…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.53,0:23:43.72,ZW,NTP,0,0,0,,真白 振作點
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.83,0:23:44.63,ZW,NTP,0,0,0,,來 蚯蚓
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.73,0:23:47.00,ZW,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 扭得真是恰到好處…喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.10,0:23:48.63,ZW,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿嘿 婆婆說過
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.74,0:23:50.57,ZW,NTP,0,0,0,,要盡量講冷笑話
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.67,0:23:52.26,ZW,NTP,0,0,0,,妳的祖母到底是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.37,0:23:54.31,ZW,NTP,0,0,0,,呃…啊 沒時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.38,0:23:54.93,ZW,NTP,0,0,0,,妳啊！
